Rating: 4
This is a new favorite of ours. Quick, easy and tastes fabulous. I have made this at least 4 times and I believe the amount of stock is exactly correct. However, if it isn't thickening quickly as it should, then you may need to mash it more thoroughly. I think the more you mash the more starch you release and the thicker the beans get. Also it always seems to get thicker as it cools. One last note - if you love cumin (as I do) be generous; I add at least 1 - 2 teaspoons and it tastes great.

